messages.messageBody:
Forwarding....

CBS has refused to play Move On's "Bush in 30 Seconds" ad during the
superbowl, siting it as "too controversial." I am dumbfounded. The one
that was voted the best is so benign compared to what we could say about
Bush. To see the winner, Child's Pay, and to send CBS a message, go here:

http://www.moveon.org/cbs/ad/
